*Taksi* vožnja je bila preko očekivane. (The taxi ride was more than expected.)

Dobro je organizovati *taksi* za ljude koji imaju potrebu za njim. (It's good to organize a taxi for people who need it.)

*Taksi* služba je potrebna u našem gradu. (Taxi service is needed in our city.)

Ona se vozila *taksijem* preko grada. (She rode a taxi across the city.)

Nemam novca da platim *taksi*. (I don't have money to pay for the taxi.)